ro</a>), Twitter (@TradeHeroMobile) or email us (<a href=\"mailto:support@tradehero.mobi\">support@tradehero.mobi</a>).\r\n\r\nThat said, if you have some improvements in mind, feel free to contact us as well. Weve received some great feedback along the way that has helped us tremendously. We know that some of you have asked us to include your local stock exchanges (Mexico and India, we hear you!) Dont worry; were on it. Were excited about the release of our Android version too!\r\n\r\nBehind every Trade Hero are the unsung heroes, the team from Singapore that has been working tirelessly to bring you this application. Our team in Singapore has largely expanded from 2 in early 2012, comprising Dinesh (our CEO) and Dominic (our CTO), to nearly 10 people now.\r\n\r\nPeter Lynch once said, Owning stocks is like having children - don\'t get involved with more than you can handle.\r\n\r\nTradeHero has, hopefully, come to the rescue.\r\n\r\nThats all for now  stay tuned for updates!','Welcome to TradeHeros Official Blog','','publish','closed','open','','welcome-to-tradeheros-official-blog','','','2013-06-21 15:59:46','2013-06-21 07:59:46','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=86',0,'post','',0),(87,4,'2013-06-13 15:54:19','2013-06-13 07:54:19','Hey there,\n\nToday marks the <i>x</i>th month since our launch on the 12<sup>th</sup> of December, 2012!\n\nOn this blog, well be posting updates, stock market news &amp; tips, articles, information on TradeHero and much more. Check it out regularly for the latest news.\n\nWeve had an incredible <i>x</i> months. TradeHeros up for its 2<sup>nd</sup> round of seed funding. Investors have generously responded and were on the right track. Weve been contacted by people from all over the globe telling us that they love this app. If youve enjoyed our app so far, rate it on the App Store or let us know on Facebook (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/TradeHero\">www.facebook.com/TradeHero</a>), Twitter (@TradeHeroMobile) or email us (<a href=\